Testing:
  - WsServer has been tested with desktop browsers:
      Firefox 68.8, Chrome 83.0, Chromium 81.0, Opera 68.0, Yandex 20.4 (MS Edge - it's unknown);
  - WssServer was tested by Chromium with “chrome://flags/#allow-insecure-localhost” enabled
      and with own secure client.

Certificates (localhost self-signed):
  From https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/technotes/guides/security/jsse/samples/index.html
    - testkeys: Java 1.7+;
  Self-made:
    - localhost.jks: Java 1.8+
